title: Primary care consultations last less than 5 minutes for half the world's population

title_detail.value: Primary care consultations last less than 5 minutes for half the world's population

summary: Primary care consultations last less than 5 minutes for half the world's population, but range from 48 seconds in Bangladesh to 22.5 minutes in Sweden, reveals the largest international study of its kind.
